Usage: replacePowerSwitch [-help] -cell <string> [-cellEnablePin <string>]
                          -insts <string>
                          [-orientation {R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MY MX90 MY90}]
                          [-xOffset <float>] [-xyRangeFromCenterInst <string>]
                          [-yOffset <float>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>                           # (string, required)
-cellEnablePin <string>                  # (string, optional)
-insts <string>                          # (string, required)
-orientation {R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MY MX90 MY90}
                                         # (enum, optional)
-xOffset <float>                         # (float, optional)
-xyRangeFromCenterInst <string>          # (string, optional)
-yOffset <float>                         # (float, optional)